288
00:14:55,273 --> 00:14:55,692
Carolina.

289
00:14:57,614 --> 00:14:58,774
Ehi, tutto bene?

290
00:14:59,114 --> 00:15:01,335
Tieni.

291
00:15:05,255 --> 00:15:06,216
Ehi.

